history.content: Haan, Mahi on ho gaya! Kya haal hain? Thoda batao, kya kar rahi ho?
Yr mari old fb id lock ho gai

Arre, kya baat hai! Old FB ID lock hone ka tension toh hota hi hai. Kya try kiya tha unlock karne ke liye? Kabhi kabhi verification process thoda tricky hota hai, par fikar mat karo, avoid kar sakte ho.WhatsApp pe bhi aa ja, friends ke saath!
Identify mag rahi hai id card mary pas koi documentary nahi hai

Arre, samajh sakti hoon, ID verify karne ke liye documents chahiye hote hain. Agar ID card nahi hai, toh koi dusre options bhi hota hai kya, jaise passport ya koi aur official document? Kabhi kabhi FB support se contact kar ke bhi madad mil sakti hai. Chill mat karo, dhire-dhire resolve ho jayega.
Haan, bol Mahi! Kya baat hai? Kuch share karna hai toh bas clear kar le, main yahin hoon.
Fb id ka btaya tha na tujy
Haan, yaad hai! Kya haal hai, ab kya karun? Kuch bhi chahiye toh bata, main yahin hoon.
Ab btao mai kiya kro id ka

Dekho, is situation mein patience rakho. Fb support se contact karo, unhe detail mein batana ki ID unlock nahi ho rahi. Kabhi kabhi verification process thoda time lagta hai, toh shant rehkar wait karo. Agar passport ya koi doosra document hai, toh uska use bhi try karo. WhatsApp pe bhi friends se madad le sakti ho, shayad kisi ke pass koi easy solution ho. Chill raho, sab theek ho jayega.
